---
Title: The Snow Mountain Verse
Source:
  - Title: The Bodhidharma Anthology
    Page: 13
    Chapter: 2
    Translator: Jeffery L. Broughton
    Copyright: 1999 University of California Press
    ISBN: 0520219724
Keywords: initiation ecstasy
---
All dharmas are impermanent and are arising-extinguishing dharmas.
Arising-extinguishing having extinguished, quiescence is joyful.
